{
  "stem": "25288.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It were pretty good shape.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So we settled then down over there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And so we happen-- we-- we have to do our living, so we did some business in the black market.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] People bought some-- some people bought some oil.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "That was very, very valuable, because there wasn't any-- any-- the-- the-- the butter, or margarine-- anything.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "That was only oil for cooking-- and took it to Budapest, or some other big city, where it was-- we liberated, and sold it, through that time.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "What I made-- what I made a living, there was a-- a-- I made cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I bought from the farmers tobacco, and cut it real fine, and-- and made cigarette; and put all the cigarette on a little box.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I don't know how there-- 200 [? bale. ?] And I still took it to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I sold it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was pharmacy-- there was a pharmacy in the town.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, I need medicine-- anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why don't you try to get some medicine in Budapest?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I solded the cigarette in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I would made, I-- what I made-- and for the money, I bought some medicine.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And I brought it down to-- to-- to Tokaj.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I sold it to their pharmacy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I did it for a while.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And somebody warned me-- don't do that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because you sell some medicine, and somebody may die from that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You are in big trouble.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So meantime, Ilona came back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were married.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I opened my family business, the-- the-- we-- we-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we'll continue in the next tape.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
